      "testStrategy": "1. Start a long session that produces > 75% of max_context_tokens. Verify that chunk_001.json appears in ~/.grok/sessions/{id}/archives/ and that the active session.messages contains the archive notice instead of the original messages.\n2. Type `/recall 1` — verify the archived context is injected back and the model can answer questions about it.\n3. Use the `recall_context` tool from within an AI turn — verify it returns the summary correctly.\n4. Run `/archives` — verify all chunk IDs + metadata are listed.\n5. Set `auto_compress = false` — verify old drop-only behaviour is restored.\n6. Simulate Starlink drop during the summarization API call — verify the archive write is atomic (no partial files) and the session continues without error.",
