      "description": "Push Grok-CLI ACP integration to parity (and beyond) with Claude/Gemini/Copilot inside Zed. Deliver a beautiful, dynamic, interactive bottom status bar + native clickable thinking traces using agent-client-protocol v0.15+ features. Goal: make Grok feel first-class in Zed.",
      "details": "## Vision\nOther agents show a rich footer/status bar with model, thinking mode, token usage, and quick actions. Thinking traces are natively collapsible and clickable. We will match (and surprise with) a hybrid **smart dynamic status line that expands into a full action bar**.\n\n## Key Deliverables\n1. **Dynamic Status Bar** (via session/update)\n   - Always-visible compact line: Model | Thinking Mode | Tokens | Context %\n   - Expands on hover/focus into a full action bar (Stop, New Chat, /think high/low/off, Model picker, Clear Context)\n2. **Native Thinking Traces**\n   - Stop sending raw <details> markdown\n   - Use structured thinking_content + session/update events for native Zed rendering\n   - Make thinking blocks clickable and expandable in real time\n3. **Live Token Meter**\n   - Update on every chunk (not just end of turn)\n   - Beautiful progress bar + exact numbers\n4. **Interactive Controls**\n   - Clicking thinking mode pill opens quick switcher\n   - Action buttons send proper ACP commands\n5. **ACP v0.15+ Features**\n   - Leverage latest protocol capabilities for better structured content and events\n\n## Architecture Notes\n- Extend protocol.rs with new update types (StatusBarUpdate, ThinkingBlockUpdate, ActionBarItem)\n- Create src/acp/status_bar.rs for building and emitting the dynamic bar\n- Hook into handle_chat_completion and streaming response path\n- Respect Session DNA for default thinking mode + model preference\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- Zed shows a persistent, updating status line at the bottom of Grok sessions\n- Clicking the thinking mode changes it live\n- Thinking traces render as native collapsible blocks (not markdown)\n- Token meter updates smoothly during generation\n- Action bar appears when focused and works\n- No regression on existing ACP functionality",
